snippet.title: Edge of Sanity - Exclusive Gameplay Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Check out the trailer for the 2D Lovecraftian survival horror game Edge of Sanity. Struggle against madness in unforgiving lands of Alaska, twisted and distorted by lovecraftian monsters. Manage your resources, make difficult choices, and most importantly, survive. Edge of Sanity is launching on PC at a later date.
